                                                      int subcircle,
                                                      java.lang.String num)
        Takes a bitmap and turns it into a circular bitmap. Also adds a counter in the bottom right corner for group size when necessary.
        Parameters:
        bitmap - The bitmap to be processed.
        subcircle - Whether or not the subcircle should exist.
        num - The number that should appear in the subcircle.
